data.description: Move-in Ready! 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in gated community. Refrigerator is included. High ceilings and lots of natural light. Master bedroom has two closets and bathroom with dual sinks and separate shower and tub. Other bedrooms are spacious. Living room has a fireplace. Backyard has a covered patio for outdoor entertaining. Close to shopping, dining, and the freeway. It would not last long!!!
